Changes since version 2.0 of Fortunate
--------------------------------------

-ported to MacOS X 10.1 (and will probably work on 10.0)
-now includes the fortune command-line program and fortune files
-set menu layout to match MacOS X standards
-preference for offensive fortunes added


Changes since version 1.0 of Fortunate
--------------------------------------

- ported to MacOS X Server, including the new text and user defaults systems
- now has a preferences panel to set the fortune program's path and the font
- the fortune path can include arguments so that you can control what fortunes you see
- exciting new info panel
